snippet.title: Amber Heard trying to silence the people #JusticeforJohnny #WejustdontlikeyouAmber #Imnotabot
snippet.description:
I'm not a bot. Can't believe Amber Heard's defensive team is trying to attack people who think she is guilty. She has tried to use the Metoo movement, LGBTQ, and other social movements for her personal gain. 

I will not stand behind a woman who is malicious and deceitful. And now to see her try to silence real people who care about Johnny as fans, it just makes me sick and angry. 

I'm already upset about the media trying to be biased. 

Johnny never deserved any of this abuse from Amber. 
 
https://afriendorfoe.home.blog/2020/08/21/heavy-on-my-heart-im-not-a-bot/

#JusticeforJohnny #Can'tsilencethepeople #I'mnotabot #Wejustdon'tlikeyouAmber
